msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pct\\_change"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:1 of
msgid "Percentage change between the current and a prior element."
msgstr "当前元素与前一个元素之间的百分比变化。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:3 of
msgid ""
"Computes the percentage change from the immediately previous row by "
"default. This is useful in comparing the percentage of change in a time "
"series of elements."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，计算与紧邻前一行的百分比变化。这在比较元素时间序列中的变化"
"百分比时非常有用。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pct_change.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:7 of
msgid "Periods to shift for forming percent change."
msgstr "用于形成百分比变化的偏移周期数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:9 of
msgid "How to handle NAs before computing percent changes."
msgstr "在计算百分比变化之前如何处理NAs。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:11 of
msgid "The number of consecutive NAs to fill before stopping."
msgstr "在停止之前要填充的连续NAs的数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:13 of
msgid "Increment to use from time series API (e.g. 'M' or BDay())."
msgstr "来自时间序列API的增量（例如 'M' 或 BDay()）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:15 of
msgid ""
"Additional keyword arguments are passed into `DataFrame.shift` or "
"`Series.shift`."
msgstr "其他关键字参数将传递给 `DataFrame.shift` 或 `Series.shift`。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pct_change.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.pct_change.pct_change:18 of
msgid "**chg** -- The same type as the calling object."
msgstr "**chg** -- 与调用对象相同的类型。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pct_change.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

